metadata.description:
Meet Planet Earth through the many eyes of travel blogging aliens Flip and Mozi. While they wait a few thousand years for a tow truck for their crash-landed spaceship, Flip and Mozi are on a mission to explore Earth, meet our planet's amazing creatures, and learn what it means to be an "earthling" along the way. From the creators of Wow in the World with original music from Grammy-nominated artists, The Pop Ups, Flip, and Mozi is an intergalactic musical adventure that brings conservation into your family conversations. Visit tinkercast.com to discover more WOWs about our world after the show.

This podcast contains ads. Yoto does not control these ads and they do not represent us or our opinions. Please listen with care.
